        {
            "title": "信義光能半年盈利跌58.8%派息降  信義能源盈利派息齊增逾20%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">信義系公布上半年業績，其中信義光能(00968)半年純利7.46億元(人民幣．下同)，按年倒退58.8%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123543_source-web_信義光能00968-4_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230719-123543_source-web_信義光能00968-4_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司擬派中期息每股4.2港仙，也較去年同期減少58%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於同系信義能源(03868)上半年度純利，則升至4.5億元，按年增長23.4%；擬派中期息每股2.9港仙，較去年同期提升26.1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15140904-%e4%bf%a1%e7%be%a9%e5%85%89%e8%83%bd%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c58-8%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af%e9%99%8d-%e4%bf%a1%e7%be%a9%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af%e9%bd%8a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-01 17:35:27",
